    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Glow Plug Assisted Start</title>
        <para>Glow plug assisted start improves engine startability in cold weather. Glow plugs are controlled by the
            ECM, which monitors the engine temperature. An amber WAIT TO START lamp informs the operator when the engine
            is ready for cranking.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
